=== EMBED AS WIDGET ON ANY WEBSITE ===

Option 1 — Simple iframe embed (full agent with sidebar):
<iframe
  src="https://YOUR-DEPLOYED-URL.com/agent"
  width="100%"
  height="700"
  style="border:none; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">
</iframe>

Option 2 — Compact widget mode (no sidebar/topbar, clean chat only):
<iframe
  src="https://YOUR-DEPLOYED-URL.com/agent?widget=1"
  width="420"
  height="620"
  style="border:none; border-radius:20px; box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); position:fixed; bottom:24px; right:24px;">
</iframe>

Option 3 — Floating chat bubble widget:
<div id="qm-widget" style="position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:9999;">
  <div id="qm-frame" style="display:none;width:420px;height:620px;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);margin-bottom:12px;">
    <iframe src="https://YOUR-DEPLOYED-URL.com/agent?widget=1" width="100%" height="100%" style="border:none;"></iframe>
  </div>
  <button onclick="var f=document.getElementById('qm-frame');f.style.display=f.style.display==='none'?'block':'none'"
    style="width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00e5ff,#7c3aed);border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:24px;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,229,255,0.4);">
    🧠
  </button>
</div>

=== URL PARAMS ===
?widget=1        → Hides sidebar and topbar, clean chat only (best for embedding)
?theme=light     → Force light theme
?theme=dark      → Force dark theme (default)
